text: Flamingokvintetten 6 is a studio album by Flamingokvintetten, released in 1975. It topped the Swedish albums chart on 27 November 1975. ==Track listing== # Sjätte September (Peter Himmelstrand) # Stupid Cupid (Neil Sedaka, Howard Greenfield) # Hälsa till Marie från mej (Peter Himmelstrand, bearbetning av Just a Closer Walk with Thee) #Misaluba (Giosy Capuano, Mario Capuano) #Alltid ensam (Mister Lonely) (Gene Allan, Bobby Vinton, Hasse Carlsson) #Lilla Angeline (Poor Little Angeline) (Will Grosz, S.
